quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  3,122,"When two groups from you started/began that they weaken and become cowardly (B) , and God (is) their (B)`s guardian and on God so should rely/depend the believers"
  3,123,"And God had (E) given you victory/aid with (at) Badr , and you are humiliated/disgraced , so fear and obey God, maybe/perhaps you thank/be grateful"
  3,124,"If/when you say to the believers: \"Is it not enough/sufficient for you that your Lord extends (supplies) you with three thousand from the angels sent descending"
